{"tid":1078752,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"信唔信緣份呢家野?","createTime":"2019-03-26T12:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T20:02:21.000Z","uid":133373,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"319f858e8d93560c84b0070924fc1fd6820ee743","tid":1078752,"uid":133373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔到你唔信。<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，自己因為返工受咗氣，所以想搵個途徑發洩下，醒起之前買咗迪迪尼年飛，所以就決定去坐過山車。坐完迪迪尼列車行去搭𨋢，之後有個人同我一齊搭。出左閘就一齊行去樂園門口入閘，以為大家會分別，點知又一齊行去space mountain排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲坐埋一齊玩，玩嘅全程大家都冇出過聲......之後就諗住分道揚鑣啦！可能有朋友等緊佢呢。我就繼續行去玩其他機動遊戲，點知去到灰熊山谷架過山車又見到佢同個啊叔坐，而我就排係佢後面，都隔得幾遠。然後我就玩咗兩次就走，走嘅同時又係度諗：走就應該唔會再見到佢掛......點知去到迪迪尼站月台又見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同一架車，同一卡。到欣澳站轉車又一齊行去香港站方向，全程都冇出過聲。但係最終我因爲追車而上咗架地鐵，而佢就冇上等下一班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緣份呢家野真係好奇妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過與其話世界真細小，其實迪迪尼仲細小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5696f0ae79b1d7d439010356dbd040420605e7","tid":1078752,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"Ok 👌"},{"pid":"43ce2c2efb9cb8b67ea60d3f4cbd5739a9f4c2d9","tid":1078752,"uid":140580,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"信<br />\n<br />\n但你呢個唔係有緣份嘅例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc23de9baf46e02f45bf71e9379ff996a3b21157","tid":1078752,"uid":133373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"43ce2c2efb9cb8b67ea60d3f4cbd5739a9f4c2d9","tid":1078752,"uid":140580,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"信<br />\n<br />\n但你呢個唔係有緣份嘅例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"希望仲有後續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f38134f2e9d7e9b11348fa1e05dcf870c66db2","tid":1078752,"uid":188148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"有，但唔會出現係我身上"},{"pid":"74f30aad20d9906efe3c37792a6cf62a0ee150d7","tid":1078752,"uid":12882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"信，但完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cfa6cb88fa09ff2f5e3d3f945bd2cf89217eba","tid":1078752,"uid":133373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46f38134f2e9d7e9b11348fa1e05dcf870c66db2","tid":1078752,"uid":188148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"有，但唔會出現係我身上"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:04:54.000Z","msg":"希望在明天"},{"pid":"01c662004ba5987787a646b29e61934e890b6aaa","tid":1078752,"uid":133373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74f30aad20d9906efe3c37792a6cf62a0ee150d7","tid":1078752,"uid":12882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"信，但完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"即使係短暫嘅緣份都充滿回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30085914e38ec7c017a35f248e919841b0758aac","tid":1078752,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01cfa6cb88fa09ff2f5e3d3f945bd2cf89217eba","tid":1078752,"uid":133373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46f38134f2e9d7e9b11348fa1e05dcf870c66db2","tid":1078752,"uid":188148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"有，但唔會出現係我身上"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:04:54.000Z","msg":"希望在明天"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"失望也在明天"},{"pid":"5a8f8abfd2e35acc